I’ve identified the concrete gap: low-signal values are contextualized today, but positioned structural features can still collapse to bare values and lose their predicate identity in audits. I’m patching shared frame-selector helpers to emit deterministic contextual audit terms (low-signal plus positioned predicates), then wiring codec and F-logic metadata to consume that shared path.
